products.description: The dried unopened flower buds of an evergreen tree, this spice is easily identified by its incredibly intense spicy aroma and pungent bittersweet flavours. Cloves are an essential spice in Eastern cuisine and are primarily used to flavour and aromatize meat or rice-based dishes.

products.name: Nuts

products.description: Simple yet effective chilli is an easily accessible avenue to pack a spicy punch into a dish.
